Rating: 3
I have this recipe memorized. I have been making it since it appeared in Bon Appetit. I make it whenever I have to feed breakfast to a crowd. Filling, easy to make, and very flavorful. I love the thyme + eggs + sausage. Usually I use a chicken-apple sausage because of a picky crowd re: meat and pork. But a spicier sausage is really good. The creaminess of the cream cheese is really good-- I prefer it to other cheeses in my eggs.

