I have been making this for my family for special breakfasts since it was first published in 97. It is THE BEST!!! I panicked when I couldn't find my recipe, so I am relieved to find it so easily online.

Rating: 1
I feel terrible being the only reviewer to absolutely detest this recipe but I have to be honest. I have a pretty high tolerance for all kinds of foods and even I could not finish eating this meal. In terms of flavor, the eggs were overwhelmed by the thyme and the green onion (and i added less than what was called for). The flavor of the sausage was completely lost. As for texture, the eggs were dry little curds with pockes of gooey white cream cheese (all cooked on a lower flame than recommended by the recipe). I will definitely not be making this again.

